1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,720
I can see it.

2
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:21,320
Hold it, my friend.

3
00:00:22,520 --> 00:00:23,560
Sit with me a while.

4
00:00:23,560 --> 00:00:35,700
Dark-furred, devious-natured, hunting that Gwaii is no simple task.

5
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:41,220
You do have some skills, but this land bites with cold.

6
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:47,020
Lack of readiness could be your undoing.

7
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:55,020
Your reunion is destined, and so is my role to teach you this little trick.

8
00:00:55,020 --> 00:01:05,400
Ah, I am extraordinary.

9
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:13,200
As is my flame, it shall help you in need, be it injury, weariness, or frostbite.

10
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:17,000
Beasts or yaowguys, none shall dare to draw near.

11
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,500
Nigh.

